text: Pietro Ubaldi (Milan, September 21 1955) is an Italian voice actor and singer and comedian. == Biogaphy == Pietro Ubaldi is born in Milan on September 21 1955. He is the italian voice of Patrick Star from Spongebob, Doraemon from Doraemon and Reinhardt from Overwatch.
